description:
Welcome to the SWmobile November social. There are no scheduled talks just good conversations with fellow members! As is tradition the first drink is on SWmobile.

If you are a first-time member and/or don't know anyone and would rather pre-meet so you arrive with others please drop us a message via meetup.com (or @scottyab twitter) and we'll arrange it.

If you are keen to speak at a future event please fill in the CFP form[ http://cfp.swmobile.org](http://cfp.swmobile.org)

See you there!
title: November Social
